      "description": "Available for the discerning enthusiast is this E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L V8\u2014the only naturally aspirated V8 in M3 history. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS to achieve an 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain delivers raw mechanical feedback. Recent preventive maintenance includes a comprehensive rod bearing service and throttle actuator replacement. The E92 chassis remains stiff, supported by the factory carbon fiber roof and a Variable M Differential Lock for superior lateral dynamics. While the car exhibits minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited use, the mechanical integrity is robust, with consistent compression and a leak-free undercarriage. This is a driver-spec machine engineered for peak atmospheric performance.",
